ED_Title: Notification by the Secretary-General under Article 12, paragraph 2, of the Charter of the United Nations
ED_DecisionText: At its 93rd plenary meeting, on 25 June 2024, the General Assembly took note of the note by the Secretary-General. (Footnote: A/78/300.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
